{
  "stem": "27770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with the wood part of the rifle, they started to scream and to knock and to beat everybody, 4:00 in the morning, out, out, out!",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rush!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had already prepared for every four of us a sack on our back, a little clothing, a little food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he wanted to knock on my head with this rifle, for them on the head, and to bring out blood was nothing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was bending down, and he knocked down my sack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the sack opened up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time already I went out to the street, the sack was empty.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't have no more shirt, no more food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started to chase us from our street from the ghetto, to the factory-- a brick factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say, roughly speaking, it took about two hours to walk there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any Hungarian neighbor, if it was a growing up person or a young person, a stick in their hand and beating us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how we arrived to this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hundreds of people had broken heads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a line of blood, the way you see a dividing line here on the road, you see a white or yellow dividing line, there was a red dividing line all over, until we arrived to the factory.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Hungarian were such a sadistic people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They made tent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If the tent would be at least so much to bend in to the bed, so at least we could bend-- they made such a low tent that a baby could go into this tent.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we didn't have to go into the tent, we had to sneak into the tent like a snake.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Was terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No facilities.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once in a while a small piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For warm food, forget it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
